{"tid":2266711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滙控計劃從法國退市 稱無礙歐洲日常業務","createTime":"2020-11-01T13:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T15:12:41.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"902039d141324473e855e8ffa049f7fb5dee7bcc","tid":2266711,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"滙控計劃從法國退市 稱無礙歐洲日常業務<br />\n<br />\n滙豐控股(<a href=\"http://00005.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00005.HK&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=2f5e3d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00005.HK</a>)發公告，指在審核交易量、成本和行政要求後，計劃向法國巴黎泛歐證券交易所提交退市申請，指除牌需獲巴黎泛歐交易所批准，不會影響滙豐在法國或歐洲的日常業務，亦不會影響滙豐在港交所、倫敦交易所、紐約交易所及百慕達證券交易所的上市。有必要時會有進一步公告。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2364231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2364231&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=528bc667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2364231</a>"},{"pid":"5515a345aae4bcb8d45adabe0255866527e07db5","tid":2266711,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"執嘅第一步"},{"pid":"f68a7e5f655adf791040638be9ea8274a03a60dc","tid":2266711,"uid":9264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T13:56:15.000Z","msg":"除牌都要批准?好似支那咁我唔俾你走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d2fbd60ebd0d42459cb59d91ac5cb696d346c8","tid":2266711,"uid":277702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:47:01.000Z","msg":"All in 支那"},{"pid":"845f70dfaf82cce0bf085af10b9420aadc112488","tid":2266711,"uid":220942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5515a345aae4bcb8d45adabe0255866527e07db5","tid":2266711,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"執嘅第一步"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T